現在是星期五了嗎？
Is it Friday already?

156
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:13,400
是的，花花公子
Yeah, lover boy.

157
00:14:13,600 --> 00:14:16,700
想被人修理嗎？來吧，我會好好疼你的
You want a piece? Jump in. I'll love you.

158
00:14:16,900 --> 00:14:20,500
那麼到底是他媽的哪個人渣搶的貨車？
So who in the goddamn piss hell stole our fucking truck?

159
00:14:21,500 --> 00:14:24,500
- 你說什麼？ - 是誰偷了那貨車？
- What did you say? - Who stole the fucking truck?

160
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:27,700
- 我不想知道 - 沒人問你，正經人
- I don't want to know. - Who asked you, workingman?

161
00:14:27,800 --> 00:14:30,500
做這事的人去死吧，我現在想知道那跛子是什麼人？
Fuck who did it. What I want to know is, who's the gimp?

162
00:14:30,600 --> 00:14:32,900
- 沒他的事  - 全是你在說，我怎麼知道？
- He's okay. - Says you. How do I know that?

163
00:14:32,900 --> 00:14:35,000
怎麼樣，拐腳佬？說說你的故事吧
What about it, pretzel man? What's your story?

164
00:14:35,100 --> 00:14:36,400
他叫「口水先生」
His name is Verbal.

165
00:14:37,100 --> 00:14:38,500
維伯·肯特
Verbal Kint.

166
00:14:38,500 --> 00:14:40,000
- 「口水先生」？ - 對
- Verbal? - Yeah.

167
00:14:40,100 --> 00:14:43,200
真名是羅傑，人人說我話太多
Roger, really. People say I talk too much.

168
00:14:43,500 --> 00:14:45,400
我正想叫你閉嘴
I was going to tell you to shut up.

169
00:14:45,500 --> 00:14:49,200
- 我們以前見過一二次 - 是在州局，我因為詐騙罪被逮進了局子
- We met before, once or twice. - In County. I was in for fraud.

170
00:14:49,300 --> 00:14:51,500
我們曾一同被指認，後來如何了？
You were in a lineup then, too. What happened?

171
00:14:51,700 --> 00:14:54,500
被判了90天，緩刑釋放
I walked. 90 days, suspended.

172
00:14:54,800 --> 00:14:57,600
- 你也不是個好人 - 好了，大家聽我說…
- So you did it. - All right, now look...

173
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:01,700
…我們都因這事被攪進來
...we've all been put out by this whole thing, right?

174
00:15:01,900 --> 00:15:05,600
我想我們該設法挽回點面子
I figure we owe it to ourselves to salvage a little dignity.

175
00:15:06,100 --> 00:15:09,400
我和范斯特聽說有樁生意
Now, me and Fenster heard about a little job.

176
00:15:09,500 --> 00:15:11,300
安靜會兒好嗎？
Why don't you just calm down?

177
00:15:11,800 --> 00:15:13,700
聽他說說又怎麼了？
What do you care what he has to say?

178
00:15:14,800 --> 00:15:16,700
我不過隨便說說
I'm just talking here.

179
00:15:17,100 --> 00:15:20,200
看來哈肯尼先生，似乎想聽我要說什麼…
It seems to me like Mr.Hockney wants to hear it...

180
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:22,200
…而我知道范斯特亦有興趣
...and I know Fenster's down.

181
00:15:23,100 --> 00:15:24,800
你呢？夥計
What about you, guy?

182
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:27,600
當然有興趣
I'm interested.

183
00:15:28,900 --> 00:15:30,100
看到沒？
There. See?

184
00:15:30,400 --> 00:15:33,500
我只想行使我的自由集會權
I'd like to exercise my right to free assembly.

185
00:15:33,700 --> 00:15:35,500
閉會兒嘴不行嗎？
Why don't you just shut up?

186
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:43,100
你是不明白
You're missing the point.

187
00:15:43,800 --> 00:15:44,900
不
No.

188
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:47,900
不明白的人是你
You're missing the point.

189
00:15:48,100 --> 00:15:50,600
我不想聽你說任何事
I don't want to hear anything from you.

190
00:15:51,100 --> 00:15:53,100
我對你的生意沒興趣
I don't care about your job.

191
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:56,100
此外…
And...

192
00:15:58,300 --> 00:16:00,800
…我不想和你們有任何關聯
...I want nothing to do with any of you.

193
00:16:01,300 --> 00:16:04,500
我很抱歉這麼說，但你們全都見鬼去吧
I beg your pardon, but you can all go to hell.

194
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:08,500
迪恩·基頓…
Dean Keaton...

195
00:16:09,200 --> 00:16:10,700
…想正經做人
...gone the high road.

196
00:16:12,300 --> 00:16:14,400
這世界是怎麼了？
What is the world coming to?

197
00:16:19,400 --> 00:16:20,600
去他的
Fuck him.

198
00:16:25,300 --> 00:16:27,000
事情就是這麼開始的:
And that was how it started:

199
00:16:27,100 --> 00:16:29,500
我們五個因為莫須有的罪名
Five of us brought in on a trumped-up charge...

200
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:31,500
…被這些低能兒關了進來
...to be leaned on by half-wits.

201
00:16:34,800 --> 00:16:37,300
在這兒我真不能多說
I really can't talk about it much here.

202
00:16:37,400 --> 00:16:41,000
警察們永遠也想不到的是…
What the cops never figured out, and what I know now...

203
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:44,300
…這些人永遠不會屈服
...was that these men would never break, never lie down.

204
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:47,300
永遠不會屈服於任何人
Never bend over for anybody.

205
00:16:48,300 --> 00:16:49,500
任何人都不行
Anybody.

206
00:16:58,666 --> 00:17:03,103
聖佩德羅  加利福尼亞  當日 


207
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:08,700
- 你是誰？ - FBI探員 傑克·拜爾
- Who are you? - Agent Jack Baer, FBI.

208
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:11,000
- 死了多少人？ - 迄今為止發現15具屍體
- How many dead? - 15 so far.

209
00:17:11,100 --> 00:17:13,900
還在繼續打撈水下的屍體
They're still pulling bodies out of the water.

210
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:16,000
- 有生還者嗎？ - 有兩個
- Any survivors? - Two.

211
00:17:16,100 --> 00:17:18,900
一個被送進了州立醫院，但他正在昏迷中
One guy's in County hospital, but he's in a coma.

212
00:17:18,900 --> 00:17:22,000
地方檢察官帶走了另一個傢伙，一個跛腳的紐約人
The DA has a second guy, a cripple from New York.

213
00:17:22,100 --> 00:17:24,500
上頭下令封鎖現場
The chief wants this place sealed off.

214
00:17:24,600 --> 00:17:27,400
要是有別的問題， 就給他們電話吧
If you have any questions, give him a call.

215
00:18:01,500 --> 00:18:04,800
我是奎恩，我去了洛杉磯，星期二才回來
This is Dave Kujan. I'll be in Los Angeles until Tuesday.

216
00:18:04,900 --> 00:18:09,100
若有急事，可聯繫聖佩德羅警署的傑夫·拉賓…
If you need to reach me, contact Jeff Rabin of the San Pedro Police Department...

217
00:18:09,200 --> 00:18:12,000
…找內線112即可，祝你順利
...at extension 112. Have a nice day.

218
00:18:15,109 --> 00:18:16,199
聖佩德羅警署  洛杉磯市


219
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:18,400
- 我為什麼不能見他？ - 我已經說了…
- Why can't I see him? - I told you...

220
00:18:18,400 --> 00:18:21,400
…地方檢察官昨晚來這裡
...the DA came down here last night ready to arraign...

221
00:18:21,500 --> 00:18:23,600
…準備等他到了，就開始提審
...even before they moved him to County.

222
00:18:23,600 --> 00:18:26,000
然後過了五分鐘，肯特的律師露面了…
Kint's lawyer shows up five minutes later...

223
00:18:26,100 --> 00:18:29,600
…地方檢察官出來的時候，像是蔫了的茄子
...the DA comes out looking like the bogeyman smacked him around.

224
00:18:29,700 --> 00:18:32,800
他們給他錄了口供，並與他達成協議
They take his statement, and they cut him a deal.

225
00:18:32,900 --> 00:18:36,900
- 他們以什麼來起訴他？ - 非法持械，是輕罪
- Did they charge him with anything? - Weapons, misdemeanor 2.

226
00:18:37,300 --> 00:18:38,700
究竟是怎麼回事？
What is that?

227
00:18:39,300 --> 00:18:42,900
這裡的事情已經全部移交給地方檢察官，明白嗎？
I give the DA credit for getting that much, you understand?

228
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:44,500
請讓一下
Excuse me, sir.

229
00:18:45,700 --> 00:18:49,700
整件事情開始有政治色彩，市長昨晚來過了
This whole thing has turned political. The mayor was here last night.

230
00:18:49,800 --> 00:18:53,100
今天早上州長也曾打電話給頭兒
The chief. This morning, the governor called, okay?

231
00:18:53,200 --> 00:18:57,400
我告訴你，這傢伙的後台很硬
I'm telling you, this guy is protected from up on high by the Prince of Darkness.

232
00:18:57,400 --> 00:18:59,900
- 記得我說的話吧 - 他什麼時候可保釋外出？
- Take my word for it. - When does he post bail?

233
00:18:59,900 --> 00:19:02,200
- 可能最多再過兩小時 - 我想要見見他
- Maybe two hours, tops. - I want to see him.

234
00:19:02,200 --> 00:19:04,100
- 不行 - 我一定得見他
- No. - I gotta see him.

235
00:19:04,200 --> 00:19:06,800
- 不，不行-- - 你得幫我
- No. I can't-- - You gotta do this for me.

236
00:19:06,900 --> 00:19:09,100
我大老遠來就是為了這事
I came a long way for this.

237
00:19:09,800 --> 00:19:11,300
請進
Dave, please.

238
00:19:14,800 --> 00:19:17,600
就算我讓你見他，他也什麼都不會說的
Even if I let you talk to him, he won't talk to you.

239
00:19:19,100 --> 00:19:21,000
他會覺得是在被審問
He's paranoid about being recorded.

240
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:23,600
- 他知道審訊室裡滿佈機關 - 我戒煙了
- He knows the rooms are wired. - I quit.

241
00:19:23,700 --> 00:19:26,700
我不是審訊他，只不過隨便談談罷了
This won't be an interrogation, just a friendly chat.

242
00:19:26,900 --> 00:19:30,000
- 他不會進審訊室的 - 那就去別的地方
- He won't go into the interrogation room. - Then someplace else.

243
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:31,200
哪裡呢？
Where?

244
00:19:33,200 --> 00:19:34,500
不行，不行
No, no.

245
00:19:34,800 --> 00:19:38,400
若這是毒品交易，那毒品呢？ 如果是謀殺，那又是誰指使的？
If this was a dope deal, where's the dope? If it was a hit, who called it?

246
00:19:38,500 --> 00:19:42,000
我相信這些問題，在你心裡已經有了答案
I'm sure you have a host of wild theories to answer all these questions.

247
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:45,400
- 你很清楚我的想法 - 這簡直太瘋狂了，而且也沒什麼意義
- You know what I think. - That's crazy, and it doesn't even matter.

248
00:19:45,500 --> 00:19:48,300
這傢伙根本不知情，他的背景也已經查出來了
The guy's got total immunity. His story checks out.

249
00:19:48,600 --> 00:19:52,900
- 他沒有你想知道的答案 - 我知道他沒有答案
- He doesn't know what you want to know. - I don't think he does, not exactly.

250
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:55,900
但事情沒有那麼簡單，相信我
But there's a lot more to his story, believe me.

251
00:19:56,300 --> 00:19:59,900
我想知道碼頭上那二十七人的死因
I wanna know why 27 men died on that pier...

252
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:04,300
這事與九千一百萬毒品有關，但現場竟找不到毒品
...for what looks to be $91 million worth of dope that wasn't there.

253
00:20:04,500 --> 00:20:07,900
此外，我想確認迪恩·基頓的死訊
And above all, I want to be sure Dean Keaton's dead.

254
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:09,700
他確實死了
He's dead.

255
00:20:10,100 --> 00:20:13,100
就給我兩小時吧，到他被保釋就結束
Come on. Two hours. Just till he makes bail.

256
00:20:13,500 --> 00:20:14,900
他們都死了
They're all dead.

257
00:20:15,000 --> 00:20:17,300
我才不在乎你說的，這個基頓有多厲害…
I don't care how tough you say Keaton was...

258
00:20:17,400 --> 00:20:20,300
…船上沒有生還的人
...nobody on that boat could've come out alive.

259
00:20:23,500 --> 00:20:26,500
- 他能說話嗎？ - 他醒來還不到一小時
- Is he talking? - He regained consciousness an hour ago.

260
00:20:26,600 --> 00:20:29,000
說了些話，但不是英語，然後就停下了
He spoke, not English, then he lapsed.

261
00:20:29,200 --> 00:20:31,600
- 是匈牙利語嗎？ - 我不知道，也許是吧
- Hungarian? - That might have been it.

262
00:20:31,700 --> 00:20:34,600
- 他們大部分是匈牙利人 - 你得把這穿上
- Most of them were Hungarians. - You gotta put this on.

263
00:20:34,600 --> 00:20:37,300
燒傷病人很容易感染病菌
Burn victims are very susceptible to infection.

264
00:20:37,800 --> 00:20:40,300
還有，那兒是禁煙的
And, of course, there's no smoking.

265
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:52,600
請戴上口罩，還有別去碰他
Keep your mask up. Please don't touch him.

266
00:20:52,700 --> 00:20:53,800
他會死嗎？
Is he gonna die?

267
00:20:53,900 --> 00:20:56,600
他全身有六成被燒傷，肋骨斷裂--
He's burned 60 percent of his body, broken ribs--

268
00:20:56,700 --> 00:20:59,300
叫醫院保安來，讓人守在門口
Call security. Put a man on the door.

269
00:20:59,400 --> 00:21:01,500
- 他會有危險？ - 對
- Is he dangerous? - Yes.

270
00:21:01,900 --> 00:21:02,900
去吧
Do it.

271
00:21:03,500 --> 00:21:04,900
快去
Do it now.

272
00:21:08,000 --> 00:21:10,400
喬爾嗎？我是拜爾，從洛杉磯給你打來的
Joel? Baer. Down at LA County.

273
00:21:10,600 --> 00:21:14,500
他們在碼頭找到的那人，叫阿科西·卡瓦什
Look, the guy they pulled out of the harbor is Arkosh Kovash.

274
00:21:14,700 --> 00:21:16,400
是的，我明白
Yes, I'm sure.

275
00:21:16,900 --> 00:21:18,600
不，他受了重傷
No, he's all fucked up.

276
00:21:20,500 --> 00:21:22,100
我聽不清
I can't hear you.

277
00:21:22,700 --> 00:21:24,800
閉會兒嘴好嗎？我在打電話
Will you shut up? I'm on the phone.

278
00:21:25,400 --> 00:21:26,400
對
Yes.

279
00:21:27,400 --> 00:21:29,300
不，直到我派人來看著他
No, not till I put a man on him.

280
00:21:29,500 --> 00:21:31,800
派個會說匈牙利語的人來
Send me someone who can speak Hungarian.

281
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:34,700
他已經醒了，這傢伙說話就像個泰國妓女
He's awake. He's talking like a Thai hooker.

282
00:21:34,800 --> 00:21:36,100
凱撒·蘇斯
Keyser Soze.

283
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:39,700
- 什麼？ - 凱撒·蘇斯！
- What? - Keyser Soze!

284
00:21:44,600 --> 00:21:45,800
這是怎麼了？
No shit?

285
00:21:47,300 --> 00:21:50,100
到法院去找丹·曼徹斯特
Call Dan Metzheiser over at Justice...

286
00:21:50,400 --> 00:21:52,700
…還有海關的大衛·奎恩
...and find Dave Kujan from Customs.

287
00:22:26,700 --> 00:22:30,000
維伯，這是海關的奎恩探員
Verbal, this is Agent Kujan from Customs.

288
00:22:30,800 --> 00:22:32,300
幸會
Nice to meet you.

289
00:22:32,400 --> 00:22:34,900
他想在你離開前問幾個問題
He wants to ask you a few questions before you go.

290
00:22:35,000 --> 00:22:38,500
- 什麼問題？ - 大部分是關於迪恩·基頓的
- What about? - About a Dean Keaton, mostly.

291
00:22:39,700 --> 00:22:42,200
但我想先從在紐約的指認談起
I'd like to start at the lineup back in New York.

292
00:22:42,300 --> 00:22:45,600
- 我能喝杯咖啡嗎？ - 稍後再說吧，先說說指認時的事
- Can I get some coffee? - In a while. Let's talk about the lineup.

293
00:22:45,800 --> 00:22:49,100
我真的很口渴，我就像小孩子那樣容易脫水
I'm really thirsty. I used to dehydrate as a kid.

294
00:22:49,100 --> 00:22:51,500
有次我尿出的小便就像鼻涕一樣
Once I got so bad my piss come out like snot.

295
00:22:51,600 --> 00:22:54,600
- 就是那種又濃又粘的-- - 我去給你弄咖啡
- It was all thick and gooey-- - I'll get your fucking coffee.

296
00:22:54,700 --> 00:22:57,200
順便幫我也沖一杯
Get me one, too, while you're at it.

297
00:23:01,600 --> 00:23:03,300
那傢伙太緊張了
That guy is tense.

298
00:23:03,600 --> 00:23:05,200
緊張足以使人致命
Tension is a killer.

299
00:23:05,300 --> 00:23:08,300
我曾經加入過在伊利諾州斯科基的一個男聲四重唱組合
I used to be in a barbershop quartet in Skokie, Illinois.

300
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:11,300
男中音就叫基普·迪斯金， 是個超級大胖子
The baritone was this guy named Kip Diskin, big fat guy.

301
00:23:11,400 --> 00:23:14,000
他每天早上都緊張的要命--
Like, orca fat. He was so stressed in the morning--

302
00:23:14,100 --> 00:23:18,100
- 我們現在是想幫你 - 謝謝，我很感激
- You know we're trying to help you. - Sure, and I appreciate that.

303
00:23:18,200 --> 00:23:21,300
我也想幫你，奎恩探員，我喜歡警察
And I wanna help you, Agent Kujan. I like cops.

304
00:23:21,400 --> 00:23:24,000
我曾夢想成為聯邦探員，可是我的--
I would've liked to have been a fed, but my CP--

305
00:23:24,000 --> 00:23:28,000
你沒對我們說實話，我知道你清楚一切
You're not tellin' us everything. I know you know something.

306
00:23:28,200 --> 00:23:30,200
我已經對地方檢察官全交待了
I told the DA everything I know.

307
00:23:32,100 --> 00:23:34,500
我知道你喜歡基頓
I know you like Keaton.

308
