- 先前的證供裡你說不知道那男人是誰   - 我知道船上肯定有毒品
- You said you didn't know who it was. - I know there was dope on that boat.

1092
01:30:16,700 --> 01:30:18,200
- 別再拖延時間   - 我沒有
- Stop stallin'. - I'm not.

1093
01:30:18,300 --> 01:30:20,900
- 你明白我想知道什麼   - 給我走開
- You know what I'm getting at. - Get out of my face.

1094
01:30:21,000 --> 01:30:23,800
我已經被豁免了，不需要再受你恐嚇
I got immunity. I don't have to take this.

1095
01:30:23,900 --> 01:30:25,600
你明白我想知道什麼
You know what I'm getting at.

1096
01:30:25,600 --> 01:30:28,200
- 我不知道你在說什麼   - 說出真相！
- I don't know what you're talking about. - The truth!

1097
01:30:28,300 --> 01:30:30,400
告訴我是誰殺了基頓
Try to tell me you saw someone kill Keaton.

1098
01:30:30,500 --> 01:30:31,500
我說了
I did.

1099
01:30:31,600 --> 01:30:33,000
你在撒謊
You're lying to me.

1100
01:30:33,100 --> 01:30:36,500
- 你知道事實真相   - 我不知道你在說什麼
- You've known this whole time. - I don't know what you're saying.

1101
01:30:36,600 --> 01:30:39,200
我看見基頓中了槍，我發誓
I did see Keaton get shot. I swear to you.

1102
01:30:39,300 --> 01:30:41,900
你為何不救他？你手上有槍
Why didn't you help him? You had a gun.

1103
01:30:42,000 --> 01:30:43,900
他可是你的朋友
He was your friend.

1104
01:30:47,800 --> 01:30:49,600
因為我害怕
Because I was afraid.

1105
01:30:51,800 --> 01:30:54,400
- 怕極了   - 你怕什麼？
- Afraid. - Afraid of what?

1106
01:30:55,500 --> 01:30:57,700
- 怕什麼--   - 我知道那是凱撒·蘇斯
- Afraid of-- - I knew it was Keyser Soze.

1107
01:30:58,000 --> 01:31:01,900
是凱撒·蘇斯，他是魔鬼的化身
It was Keyser Soze, I mean, the Devil himself.

1108
01:31:03,200 --> 01:31:05,800
你怎麼敢在魔鬼的背後開槍？
How do you shoot the Devil in the back?

1109
01:31:10,300 --> 01:31:12,000
要是射不中又如何？
What if you miss?

1110
01:31:17,100 --> 01:31:19,600
那說回碼頭的事
Let's get back to the pier.

1111
01:32:42,400 --> 01:32:45,800
- 聽說過阿爾圖羅·馬奎斯嗎？   - 誰？沒有
- Arturo Marquez. Ever hear of him? - What? No.

1112
01:32:46,000 --> 01:32:48,600
他是司法部的線人
He was a stool pigeon for the Justice Department.

1113
01:32:48,700 --> 01:32:51,000
他向聯邦執行官錄了份口供
He swore out a statement to federal marshals...

1114
01:32:51,100 --> 01:32:54,500
…說他見過並能認出…
...saying that he had seen and could positively identify one...

1115
01:32:54,600 --> 01:32:55,800
凱撒·蘇斯
...Keyser Soze

1116
01:32:56,300 --> 01:32:58,100
這報告中還記載著
It says right here in the report.

1117
01:32:58,100 --> 01:33:00,900
他熟知凱撒·蘇斯一切業務…
He had intimate knowledge of his businesses, including...

1118
01:33:01,000 --> 01:33:04,200
包括運毒及謀殺以外的事情
...but not exclusive to, drug trafficking and murder.

1119
01:33:04,200 --> 01:33:05,800
我從未聽說過他
I never heard of him.

1120
01:33:05,800 --> 01:33:08,700
他的手下把他出賣給匈牙利黨
His own people were selling him to a gang of Hungarians.

1121
01:33:08,700 --> 01:33:12,400
這班匈牙利人似乎被蘇斯清除並趕回土耳其
Most likely the same Hungarians that Soze all but wiped out back in Turkey.

1122
01:33:12,700 --> 01:33:14,400
那錢並不是用來買毒品的
The money wasn't there for dope.

1123
01:33:14,500 --> 01:33:16,800
這班匈牙利人會收買…
The Hungarians were going to buy the one guy...

1124
01:33:16,900 --> 01:33:19,000
一個能把凱撒·蘇斯治罪的人
...that could incriminate Keyser Soze.

1125
01:33:19,400 --> 01:33:21,900
- 我說了我從未聽過他   - 但基頓聽過
- I said I never heard of him. - But Keaton did.

1126
01:33:22,000 --> 01:33:25,000
伊迪·菲娜琳是馬奎斯引渡案的顧問
Edie Finneran was Marquez's extradition advisor.

1127
01:33:25,100 --> 01:33:27,300
她知道他是誰，還知道他掌握的資料
She knew who he was and what he knew.

1128
01:33:27,600 --> 01:33:30,800
船上根本沒有毒品，這只是次謀殺行動
There were no drugs on that boat. It was a hit.

1129
01:33:31,000 --> 01:33:33,500
這次自殺式的行動
A suicide mission to whack out the one guy...

1130
01:33:33,600 --> 01:33:35,700
…目的是去幹掉這個能指證凱撒·蘇斯的傢伙
...that could finger Keyser Soze.

1131
01:33:36,000 --> 01:33:37,900
於是蘇斯派了班賊去執行
So Soze put some thieves to it...

1132
01:33:38,300 --> 01:33:40,700
他算好了這班人一定會死
...men he knew he could march into certain death.

1133
01:33:41,000 --> 01:33:43,500
你說蘇斯利用我們去殺人？
You're saying Soze sent us to kill someone?

1134
01:33:44,800 --> 01:33:47,800
我說就是基頓本人，他把你留在後面是有原因的
I'm saying Keaton did. He left you behind for a reason.

1135
01:33:47,900 --> 01:33:49,400
按我說的去做
Just do what I tell you.

1136
01:33:49,500 --> 01:33:52,700
既然無論跑到何處，蘇斯都能找到你…
If you all knew that Soze could find you anywhere...

1137
01:33:52,800 --> 01:33:54,700
…為何還給你金錢逃亡？
...why did he give you the money to run?

1138
01:33:54,800 --> 01:33:58,100
- 他可以在船上就把我幹掉   - 他不想我死
- He could have used you on the boat. - He wanted me to live.

1139
01:33:59,800 --> 01:34:02,400
一個過去的貪污警察
A one-time dirty cop without a loyalty in the world...

1140
01:34:02,500 --> 01:34:05,800
…竟然有顆挽救跛子賊的善心？
...finds it in his heart to save a worthless rat cripple?

1141
01:34:05,900 --> 01:34:07,300
這不可能，先生，你能給我理由嗎？
No, sir. Why?

1142
01:34:08,100 --> 01:34:09,100
是因為伊迪
Edie.

1143
01:34:09,200 --> 01:34:11,800
我從頭到尾就不信這個改過自新的故事
I don't buy that reform story for a minute.

1144
01:34:11,900 --> 01:34:13,200
就算我信這點…
Even if I did...

1145
01:34:13,300 --> 01:34:16,900
…我也不會相信他會派你去保護她
...I certainly don't believe he would send you to protect her.

1146
01:34:17,200 --> 01:34:18,400
給我個解釋？
So why?

1147
01:34:20,900 --> 01:34:22,700
因為我們是朋友
Because he was my friend.

1148
01:34:22,800 --> 01:34:26,700
不，他不是你的朋友，基頓沒有任何朋友
No, he wasn't your friend. Keaton didn't have friends.

1149
01:34:26,800 --> 01:34:28,200
你來這兒幹什麼？
What are you doing here?

1150
01:34:28,300 --> 01:34:31,000
他留下你的命，是因為他用的到你
He saved you because he wanted it that way.

1151
01:34:31,100 --> 01:34:32,200
這就是他的目的
It was his will.

1152
01:34:32,800 --> 01:34:35,500
- 基頓就是凱撒·蘇斯   - 不是
- Keaton was Keyser Soze. - No.

1153
01:34:35,500 --> 01:34:39,100
只有他才能幹掉哈肯尼和麥克麥納斯這類角色
A man who could wrangle the wills of men like Hockney and McManus.

1154
01:34:39,200 --> 01:34:44,500
只有他才能輕鬆的在警局裡安排指認
A man who could engineer a police lineup...through all his years of contacts in NYPD.

1155
01:34:44,600 --> 01:34:47,100
只有他才會殘忍的殺害伊迪·菲娜琳
The kind of man who could've killed Edie Finneran.

1156
01:34:52,100 --> 01:34:55,000
她的屍體昨天在賓夕法尼亞州一間酒店被發現
She was found yesterday at a hotel in Pennsylvania...

1157
01:34:55,100 --> 01:34:56,900
…頭部連中兩槍而亡
...shot twice in the head.

1158
01:35:01,800 --> 01:35:04,700
現在你對基頓有何看法？
What do you think about Keaton now?

1159
01:35:06,000 --> 01:35:07,000
伊迪死了？
Edie?

1160
01:35:07,000 --> 01:35:09,300
他利用你們掩護他上船
He used all of you to get him on that boat.

1161
01:35:09,300 --> 01:35:12,700
這事他本來一個人做不了，他必須要親自下手…
He couldn't get on alone. He had to pull the trigger himself...

1162
01:35:12,800 --> 01:35:14,700
…以確認幹掉了那個…
...to make sure he got his man...

1163
01:35:14,800 --> 01:35:16,900
…能指認他的傢伙
...the one man that could identify him.

1164
01:35:18,000 --> 01:35:19,600
全是胡說
This is all bullshit.

1165
01:35:19,800 --> 01:35:21,800
你說親眼看見他死了
You said you saw him die.

1166
01:35:24,200 --> 01:35:25,200
肯定嗎？
Or did you?

1167
01:35:25,400 --> 01:35:27,800
聽到警車來到時，你想藏起來
You had to hide when you heard the police cars.

1168
01:35:27,900 --> 01:35:30,300
你說在起火前聽到槍聲…
You said you heard the shot before the fire...

1169
01:35:30,700 --> 01:35:32,700
…可你沒看見他死
...but you didn't see him die.

1170
01:35:33,000 --> 01:35:35,800
- 我瞭解他，他絕不會--   - 他是在利用你
- I knew him. He would never-- - He programmed you.

1171
01:35:35,900 --> 01:35:38,500
他安排由你來說整個騙局
He programmed you to tell us what he wanted you to.

1172
01:35:38,600 --> 01:35:40,800
就如你說的，他知道我們問不出什麼來
He knew we were close. You said it yourself.

1173
01:35:40,900 --> 01:35:43,900
保你出去的政治壓力由何而來？
Where was the political pressure to protect you from?

1174
01:35:44,200 --> 01:35:45,200
就是基頓在幕後
It was Keaton.

1175
01:35:45,300 --> 01:35:48,600
- 被豁免就是給你的獎賞    - 但為什麼偏偏是我？
- Immunity was your reward. - But why me?

1176
01:35:49,200 --> 01:35:51,300
為什麼不挑范斯特，或是麥克麥納斯和哈肯尼？
Why not Fenster or McManus or Hockney?

1177
01:35:51,400 --> 01:35:54,100
為什麼是我？ 我又蠢又跛，為什麼是我？
Why me? I'm stupid. I'm a cripple. Why me?

1178
01:35:54,100 --> 01:35:55,600
就因為你是個跛子
Because you're a cripple.

1179
01:35:56,100 --> 01:35:57,800
就因為你很愚蠢
Because you're stupid.

1180
01:35:58,100 --> 01:36:00,000
就因為你比他們沒用
Because you're weaker than them.

1181
01:36:04,300 --> 01:36:05,600
要是他死了….
If he's dead...

1182
01:36:06,100 --> 01:36:10,000
要是你說的是真的，那麼就沒問題了
If what you say is true, then it won't matter.

1183
01:36:11,500 --> 01:36:14,400
襲擊警車是不是他的主意？
It was his idea to hit the taxi service, wasn't it?

1184
01:36:14,500 --> 01:36:17,600
- 對我說實話    - 是基頓提出的
- Come on, tell me the truth. - It was all Keaton.

1185
01:36:18,900 --> 01:36:21,500
我們一直跟著他
We followed him from the beginning.

1186
01:36:23,200 --> 01:36:24,400
我不知道
I didn't know.

1187
01:36:24,900 --> 01:36:26,600
我看到他死了
I saw him die.

1188
01:36:27,500 --> 01:36:30,500
我也相信他已經死了
I believe he's dead. Christ.

1189
01:36:31,700 --> 01:36:33,500
你單獨一人會不安全
You're not safe on your own.

1190
01:36:37,600 --> 01:36:38,800
你認為他是….
You think he's...

1191
01:36:39,200 --> 01:36:40,700
凱撒·蘇斯
Keyser Soze?

1192
01:36:41,500 --> 01:36:43,200
我不知道
I don't know.

1193
01:36:44,700 --> 01:36:48,600
凱撒·蘇斯只是個化名， 或就如你說的，是個傳說
Keyser Soze's a shield, or like you said, a spook story.

1194
01:36:49,700 --> 01:36:53,300
但我很瞭解基頓，你一出去就有人等著幹掉你
But I know Keaton, and someone is out there pulling strings for you.

1195
01:36:54,100 --> 01:36:57,500
- 別出去，讓我們保護你    - 我才不當誘餌，我已經自由了
- Stay here and let us protect you. - I'm not bait. I post today.

1196
01:36:57,800 --> 01:36:59,200
二十分鐘前你就可以走了
You posted 20 minutes ago.

1197
01:36:59,800 --> 01:37:01,900
裡歐隊長想你盡快離開這裡
Capt. Leo wants you out of here.

1198
01:37:02,100 --> 01:37:05,100
- 除非你想翻供   - 我會把握機會的，謝了
- Unless you turn state's. - I'll take my chances.

1199
01:37:05,400 --> 01:37:09,100
如果有人想要幹掉你，那他們一定要選在外面下手
If someone wants to get you, they're gonna get you out there.

1200
01:37:09,200 --> 01:37:12,600
若你改變口供，就再也不用害怕
Turn state's evidence. You might never see trial.

1201
01:37:12,700 --> 01:37:13,900
也許如此
Maybe so.

1202
01:37:15,500 --> 01:37:17,400
可我不是叛徒
But I'm not a rat.

1203
01:37:34,100 --> 01:37:35,700
該死的警察
Fuckin' cops.

1204
01:38:00,200 --> 01:38:02,800
能借用你的傳真機嗎？
Excuse me, can I use your fax machine?

1205
01:38:06,700 --> 01:38:09,400
請在這兒簽個名，肯特先生
You'll have to sign for these, Mr.Kint.

1206
01:38:11,600 --> 01:38:13,200
一塊金錶
One watch, gold.

1207
01:38:13,700 --> 01:38:15,800
金打火機
One cigarette lighter, gold.

1208
01:38:16,700 --> 01:38:18,600
一包煙，謝謝
One pack of cigarettes. Thank you.

1209
01:38:19,300 --> 01:38:21,300
我們仍是一無所知
We still got nothing.

1210
01:38:21,600 --> 01:38:23,900
我知道了關於基頓的事
I know what I wanted to know about Keaton.

1211
01:38:23,900 --> 01:38:25,600
那毫無價值
Which is nothing.

1212
01:38:26,100 --> 01:38:29,600
沒關係，他很快會知道我們瞭解了多少
No matter. He'll have to know how close we came.

1213
01:38:30,100 --> 01:38:32,700
不管凱撒·蘇斯存不存在
Keyser Soze or no Keyser Soze...

1214
01:38:33,100 --> 01:38:36,000
…只要基頓還活著，他就不會再出現了
...if Keaton is alive, he's not comin' up again.

1215
01:38:36,500 --> 01:38:38,300
我會去找他
I'll find him.

1216
01:38:38,700 --> 01:38:40,200
那是浪費時間
Waste of time.

1217
01:38:43,000 --> 01:38:45,400
若是傳聞不會平息， 那就不算是傳聞了
A rumor's not a rumor that doesn't die.

1218
01:38:45,800 --> 01:38:47,000
什麼？
What?

1219
01:38:48,100 --> 01:38:49,100
沒什麼
Nothing.

1220
01:38:51,100 --> 01:38:52,900
夥計，你這兒真夠亂的
Man, you're a slob.

1221
01:38:53,000 --> 01:38:55,300
但東西擺放的都還有規律
But it all has a system.

1222
01:38:56,200 --> 01:39:00,600
要是全擺的整整齊齊的，就沒有親和力了
It all makes sense if you look at it right. You gotta stand back from it.

1223
01:39:01,900 --> 01:39:05,000
要看更恐怖的地方嗎？到我車庫去就知道了
You wanna see a real horror show? See my garage.

1224
01:39:42,400 --> 01:39:44,400
說服我，告訴我每個細節
Convince me. Tell me every last...

1225
01:39:44,500 --> 01:39:47,500
我曾經加入過在伊利諾州斯科基的一個男聲四重唱組合…
When I was in that barbershop quartet in Skokie, Illinois...

1226
01:39:47,600 --> 01:39:51,100
- 你到底有沒有大腦？   - 我們需要先思考周全，再想想
- Where's your head? - We need to think, think back.

1227
01:39:51,200 --> 01:39:52,800
我肯定你們已聽過不少傳言
I'm sure you've heard tall tales.

1228
01:39:52,900 --> 01:39:54,500
- 是布裡克·馬林   - 這事不對勁
- Bricks Marlin. - This isn't right.

1229
01:39:54,600 --> 01:39:57,000
- 我想聽聽你的故事   - 已經全說了
- I just wanna hear your story. - It's all there.

1230
01:39:57,100 --> 01:40:00,500
- 我說的都是實話   - 來自加州的，名叫雷德福特
- I'm tellin' it straight. - Some guy in California called Redfoot.

1231
01:40:00,600 --> 01:40:03,100
- 這是蘇斯先生送上的禮物   - 老實對我說
- A gift from Mr.Soze. - Talk to me.

1232
01:40:03,200 --> 01:40:06,200
- 那雷德福特呢？   - 雷德福特先生並不知情匯報
- What about Redfoot? - Mr.Redfoot knew nothing.

1233
01:40:06,300 --> 01:40:09,300
- 利用不知情的人…   - 是個超級大胖子
- Using pawns... - A big fat guy. Like, orca fat.

1234
01:40:09,300 --> 01:40:11,100
還有個律師…
There was a lawyer...

1235
01:40:11,400 --> 01:40:12,800
叫小林
Kobayashi...

1236
01:40:13,300 --> 01:40:16,400
我曾在危地馬拉嘗過咖啡豆磨的新鮮咖啡
When I was picking beans in Guatemala we made fresh coffee.

1237
01:40:16,500 --> 01:40:19,500
- 我知道你認為他是好人 - 我知道他很好
- I know you thought he was a good man. - I know he was good.

1238
01:40:21,900 --> 01:40:24,800
- 告訴我全部的細節 - 這事怪極了
- You tell me every last detail. - The strangest thing.

1239
01:40:24,800 --> 01:40:26,800
你怎麼敢在魔鬼的背後開槍？
How do you shoot the Devil in the back?

1240
01:40:26,800 --> 01:40:30,100
這傢伙的後台很硬
This guy is protected from up on high by the Prince of...

1241
01:40:30,200 --> 01:40:32,500
說說你的故事，拐腳佬
What's your story, pretzel man?

1242
01:40:32,600 --> 01:40:34,400
- 還有個律師    - 什麼律師？
- There was a lawyer. - What lawyer?

1243
01:40:34,500 --> 01:40:35,600
我就是小林
I am Mr.Kobayashi.

1244
01:40:35,700 --> 01:40:39,200
- 小林，小林，   - 告訴我所有的細節
- Kobayashi. Kobayashi. - Tell me every last detail.

1245
01:40:39,300 --> 01:40:42,500
- 我為凱撒·蘇斯做事，   - 說服我，說服我
- I work for Keyser Soze. - Convince me. Convince me.

1246
01:40:57,800 --> 01:41:00,400
所有犯罪的大小角色
Every creep and scumbag that works the street...

1247
01:41:00,500 --> 01:41:02,600
…都會知道維伯·肯特的大名
...will know the name of Verbal Kint.

1248
01:41:03,300 --> 01:41:04,700
你見過那跛子嗎？
The cripple, did you see him?

1249
01:41:04,800 --> 01:41:07,900
- 那跛子！他朝那裡走了？ - 他往那邊去了
- The cripple! Which way did he go? - He went out that way.

1250
01:41:08,000 --> 01:41:10,600
我知道你知情，我還知道你沒說實話…
I know you know something. I know you're not telling...

1251
01:41:10,700 --> 01:41:11,800
我比你聰明
I'm smarter than you...

1252
01:41:11,900 --> 01:41:14,400
…不管你是否願意，我都會找到我要的答案
...and I'm gonna find out whether you like it or not.

1253
01:41:14,500 --> 01:41:16,400
警察是不會接受複雜的解釋的
To a cop, the explanation is never complicated.

1254
01:41:16,400 --> 01:41:18,000
- 總是那麼容易受騙   - 真相
- It's always simple. - The truth!

1255
01:41:18,100 --> 01:41:21,000
根本就沒什麼幕後主使
There's no arch-criminal behind it all.

1256
01:41:21,100 --> 01:41:23,900
那個人有這能力，能夠掌握…
Somebody with power, somebody who is capable...

1257
01:41:24,100 --> 01:41:25,700
凱撒·蘇斯
Keyser Soze!

1258
01:41:26,500 --> 01:41:31,900
你以為像他這樣的人會束手就擒嗎？
You think a guy like that gets this close to getting caught...and sticks his head out?

1259
01:41:32,800 --> 01:41:35,800
就是因為你愚蠢，就因為你是跛子
Because you're stupid. Because you're a cripple.

1260
01:41:35,900 --> 01:41:38,000
現在我想知道那跛子是誰？
What I wanna know is, who's the gimp?

1261
01:41:38,100 --> 01:41:40,500
你完全知道事實真相
You've known the whole fuckin' time.

1262
01:41:40,500 --> 01:41:44,200
要是他來也是要找我， 我肯定基頓已經死了
If he comes up for anything it'll be for me. I'm sure Keaton is dead.

1263
01:41:44,200 --> 01:41:47,200
我的雙腿沒有知覺，凱撒
I can't feel my legs, Keyser.

1264
01:41:47,400 --> 01:41:49,800
幹這行我學會的第一件事知道是什麼嗎？
First thing I learned on the job. You know what?

1265
01:41:49,900 --> 01:41:53,400
- 就是如何辨認兇手   - 你見到那個跛子了嗎？
- How to spot a murderer. - You got the cripple in there?

1266
01:41:53,500 --> 01:41:56,200
- 他有提到凱撒·蘇斯嗎？   - 誰？
- Did he mention Keyser Soze? - Who?

1267
01:41:56,500 --> 01:41:58,000
那之後…
After that...

1268
01:41:58,500 --> 01:42:01,500
…我猜之後再聽不到他的消息
...my guess is you'll never hear from him again.

1269
01:42:22,000 --> 01:42:27,219
最巧妙之處就是能讓人相信他不存在
The greatest trick the Devil ever pulled...was convincing the world he didn't exist.

1270
01:42:29,100 --> 01:42:30,300
然後就像那樣…
And like that...

1271
01:42:32,100 --> 01:42:33,400
…消失的無影無蹤
...he's gone
